726889f-b.title: Queens: Hollis Avenue - 201st Street
726889f-b.text:
Hollis Ave., south side, in line of 20lst Street, showing in
a set of three views, viewed in a northwesterly direction, the Elias
Hendrickson house of 1860. Some of the other owners were E.J.
Hendrickson, 1873: E. Hendrickson, 1891; Ph. Muller, 1896; and Cornelius
Remsen in 1925.
1922.
View 2: May 1923.
View 3: April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

726891f-a.title: Queens: Hollis Avenue - 201st Street
726891f-a.text:
Hollis Ave., south side, in lline of 2Olst Street, showing the
E.J. Hendrickson House of 1873. Other owners were E. Hendrickson,
1860; another of the same name, 1891, and Ph. Miller in 1896.
201st Street will extend through the left wing of the house seen in
View No. 1, which is viewed eastward. No. 2 is viewed in a southwest-
erly direction.
May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
